#Soalan 7 (Penukaran unit)
#Create a Python program that receives a temperature in Celsius and converts it to Fahrenheit.
#Formula:
#F = (C Ã— 9/5) + 32
celsius_input = input("Enter temperature in Celsius: ")
celsius = float(celsius_input)
fahrenheit = (celsius * 9/5) + 32
print(f"\n{celsius:.2f} degrees Celsius is equal to {fahrenheit:.2f} degrees Fahrenheit.")
